  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to investigate wether the adjuvant (postoperative) administration of
      acetazolamide can improve the surgical results after uvulopalatopharyngoplasty in patients
      with mild sleep apnea.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
